        <title>Characteristics of EI - Review and Reflection</title>
        <contents>&lt;div style="width: 716px;"&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In this section we have examined the question "&lt;em&gt;What is Explicit Instruction?&lt;/em&gt;"&lt;/strong&gt;  We've found it to be a &lt;em&gt;direct approach&lt;/em&gt; to teaching that outlines how to plan and deliver instruction on almost any topic.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Explicit Instruction is:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="O1"&gt;– Structured&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="O1"&gt;– Systematic&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="O1"&gt;– Flexible&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="O1"&gt;– Responsive to the needs of adult learners&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="O1"&gt;– Research-based&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Within the limits of an online course format, this course was designed with these characteristics in mind. As you move through the course readings and activities, you should see characteristics of this &lt;em&gt;direct approach&lt;/em&gt; to instruction reflected in how course material is delivered to you and/or the activities you are asked to complete.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="O1"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Now we ask you to pause and reflect on what you have learned.&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="color: #800080;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;You will be asked to post your thoughts to a discussion forum.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="O1"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #800080;"&gt;&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="O1"&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="O1"&gt;&lt;img width="54" height="50" style="float: left; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px;" alt="Reflection Icon - dark head profile with puzzle brain" src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/LTA-EI-Reflecticonsm.jpg" /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Considering the above characteristics of Explicit Instruction, which two are most compatible with your current teaching methods? Why?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="O1"&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="O1"&gt;&lt;span style="background-color: #ffff00;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #993300;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="background-color: #ffffff;"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
